DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Projetos
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Todos os Projetos","WidgetType":"grid","WidgetFilterField":"ProjectId","WidgetColor":"","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":0,"WidgetRows":23,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"showPeriodChooser":false,"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":true,"Metrics":[{"visible":true,"metricName":"Consumido","metricFieldValue":"BillableHoursGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Planejado","metricFieldValue":"PlannedHoursGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Contratado","metricFieldValue":"ContractedHoursGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"R$ Consumidos","metricFieldValue":"BillableHoursIncomeGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"R$ Planejados","metricFieldValue":"PlannedHoursIncomeGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"R$ Contratados","metricFieldValue":"ContractedHoursIncomeGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"% R$ Contratado","metricFieldValue":"BillableContractedIncomePercentageGrandTotal"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Contrato","metricFieldValue":"ContractName"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Tipo","metricFieldValue":"ContractType"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Responsável","metricFieldValue":"UserName"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Início Contrato","metricFieldValue":"StartDate"},{"visible":true,"metricName":"Fim Contrato","metricFieldValue":"EndDate"}]},"showSubTitle":true,"showTitle":true},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"with ContractEstimateRates As
(
	select	eid.Department, 
			eid.UserTypologyGroup, 
			eid.[User],
			Max(eid.UnitPriceIncome) as UnitPriceIncome
	from	Estimate e,
			EstimateItem ei,
			EstimateItemDetail eid
	where	ei.Estimate = e.Oid and
			eid.EstimateItem = ei.Oid and 
			eid.[Type] = 2 and
			e.GCRecord is null and
			e.[Contract] = @ContractId
	group by eid.Department, eid.UserTypologyGroup, eid.[User]
),
ContractTotals as
(
	select	e.Contract as ContractId,
			sum(eid.[Hours] * ei.Retainer) as ContractedHours,
			sum(eid.[Hours] * ei.Retainer * ISNULL(eid.UnitPriceIncome, 0)) as ContractedHoursIncome
	from	Estimate e,
			EstimateItem ei,
			EstimateItemDetail eid,
			WorkflowState ws,
			WorkflowStateType wst
	where	e.GCRecord is null and
			e.[Contract] = @ContractId and
			ws.Oid = e.WorkflowState and
			wst.Oid = ws.WorkflowStateType and
			wst.Status = 10 and
			ei.Estimate = e.Oid and
			eid.EstimateItem = ei.Oid and
			eid.[Type] = 2
	group by e.Contract
)
select	c.[Name] as ContractName, 
        jt.[Name] as ContractType,
		convert(varchar, c.StartDate, 106) as StartDate,
        convert(varchar, c.EndDate, 106) as EndDate,
        ssu.[UserName],
		prj.NameAndExternalId as Project,
		v.ProjectId, 
		usr.Name as OwnerName,
        usr.Oid as OwnerId,
        usr.HasImage as OwnerHasImage,
		ws.Name as Stage,
        isnull(ws.Color, wst.Color) as StageColor,
		sum(v.[ActualHours]) as [ActualHours],
		sum(v.ActualHoursCost) as ActualHoursCost,
		sum(v.ActualHoursIncome) as ActualHoursIncome,
		sum(v.[BillableHours]) as BillableHours,
		sum(v.BillableHoursIncome) as BillableHoursIncome,
		max(ct.ContractedHours) as ContractedHours,
		max(ct.ContractedHoursIncome) as ContractedHoursIncome,
		sum(v.PlannedHours) as PlannedHours,
		sum(v.PlannedHoursIncome) as PlannedHoursIncome,
		(max(ct.ContractedHoursIncome) - sum(v.ActualHoursCost)) as ContractedActualIncomeVariation,
		iif(max(ct.ContractedHoursIncome) > 0, sum(v.BillableHoursIncome) / max(ct.ContractedHoursIncome), 0.0) as ActualContractedIncomePercentage,
		iif(sum(v.PlannedHoursIncome) > 0, sum(v.BillableHoursIncome) / sum(v.PlannedHoursIncome), 0.0) as ActualPlannedIncomePercentage,
		sum(sum(v.[BillableHours])) OVER () as BillableHoursGrandTotal,
		sum(sum(v.[PlannedHours])) OVER () as PlannedHoursGrandTotal,
		max(max(ct.[ContractedHours])) OVER () as ContractedHoursGrandTotal,
		max(max(ct.ContractedHoursIncome)) OVER () as ContractedHoursIncomeGrandTotal,
		sum(sum(v.PlannedHoursIncome)) OVER () as PlannedHoursIncomeGrandTotal,
		sum(sum(v.BillableHoursIncome)) OVER () as BillableHoursIncomeGrandTotal,
		iif(max(max(ct.[ContractedHoursIncome])) OVER () > 0, sum(sum(v.[BillableHoursIncome])) OVER () / max(max(ct.[ContractedHoursIncome])) OVER (), 0.0) * 100 as BillableContractedIncomePercentageGrandTotal
from	(
		SELECT
		t.ProjectId,
		sum(t.[Hours]) as [ActualHours],
		sum(ISNULL(t.TotalUserCost, 0)) as ActualHoursCost,
		sum(t.[Hours] * ISNULL(t.UnitPriceIncome, 0)) as ActualHoursIncome,
		sum((t.[Hours] - (t.NewBusinessHours + t.AdministrativeHours))) as BillableHours,
		sum((t.[Hours] - (t.NewBusinessHours + t.AdministrativeHours)) * ISNULL(t.UnitPriceIncome, 0)) as BillableHoursIncome,
		0 as PlannedHours,
		0 as PlannedHoursIncome
		from (
				select
					t.ProjectId,
					t.UserDepartmentId as DepartmentId,
					t.Department,
					utg.Oid as TypologyGroupId,
					p.[Contract] as ProjectContractId,
					utg.[Name] as TypologyGroup,
					ISNULL(eidu.UnitPriceIncome, ISNULL(eidt.UnitPriceIncome, 0)) as UnitPriceIncome,
					iif(t.IsAdministrative = 1, (t.[Hours] / 60.0), 0) as AdministrativeHours,
					IIF(
						(
							case 
								when t.IsAdministrative = 0 and 
								(
									isnull(jc.Billable, 0) = 0 and 
									isnull(pc.Billable, 0) = 0
								)
								then 1 
								else 0 
							end
						) = 1, (t.[Hours] / 60.0), 0
					) as NewBusinessHours,
					IIF(
					(
						case 
							when t.IsAdministrative = 0 and 
							(
								(pc.Billable = 1 and isnull(jc.Billable, 0) = 0)
							) 
							then (t.[Hours] / 60.0) 
							else 0 
						end
						) = 1, (t.[Hours] / 60.0), 0
					) as InternalWorkHours,
					IIF(
					(
						case
							when t.IsAdministrative = 0 and 
							(
								(pc.Billable = 1 or jc.Billable = 1)
							)
							then (t.[Hours] / 60.0) 
							else 0 
						end
						) = 1, (t.[Hours] / 60.0), 0
					) as BillableHours,
					(t.[Hours] / 60.0) as [Hours],
					t.TotalUserCost
				from	dbo.SkillTimesheetExpanded t
						inner join Project p ON (p.Oid = t.ProjectId AND p.[Contract] = @ContractId)
						left outer join ProjectClassification pc on (pc.Oid = p.Classification)
						left outer join Deliverable d on (d.Oid = t.DeliverableId)
						left outer join JobClassification jc on (jc.Oid = d.Classification)
						left outer join UserTypology tp on (tp.Oid = t.UserTypologyId)
						left outer join UserTypologyGroup utg on (utg.Oid = tp.UserTypologyGroup)
						left outer join ContractEstimateRates eidu on (eidu.Department = t.UserDepartmentId AND eidu.UserTypologyGroup = utg.Oid AND eidu.[User] = t.CreatedBy)
						left outer join ContractEstimateRates eidt on (eidt.Department = t.UserDepartmentId AND eidt.UserTypologyGroup = utg.Oid AND eidt.[User] is null)
	) t
	group by t.ProjectId
			union all
			select	p.Oid as ProjectId,	
					0 as [ActualHours],
					0 as ActualHoursCost,
					0 as ActualHoursIncome,
					0 as BillableHours,
					0 as BillableHoursIncome,
					SUM((ISNULL(pht.PlannedMinutes, 0) / 60.0)) as PlannedHours,
					SUM((ISNULL(pht.PlannedMinutes, 0) / 60.0) * pht.SellRate) as PlannedHoursIncome
			FROM	dbo.PlannedHoursTotal pht,
					Project p
			where	pht.GCRecord is null
					AND p.Oid = pht.Project
					and p.[Contract] = @ContractId
			group by p.Oid
) v, ContractTotals ct, [Contract] c,
		JobType jt,
		Project prj,
		[User] usr,
		WorkflowState ws,
		WorkflowStateType wst,
        SecuritySystemUser ssu
where	c.Oid = @ContractId and
		ct.ContractId = @ContractId and
		ssu.Oid = c.[Owner] and
		prj.Oid = v.ProjectId and
		prj.Contract = c.Oid and
		jt.Oid = c.JobType and
		usr.Oid = c.Owner and
		ws.Oid = prj.WorkflowState and
        wst.Oid = ws.WorkflowStateType 
GROUP BY c.[Name], c.StartDate, c.EndDate, ssu.[UserName], jt.[Name], prj.NameAndExternalId, v.ProjectId, usr.Name, usr.Oid, usr.HasImage, ws.Name, ws.Color, wst.Color"}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"Sort":{"Type":1,"FieldName":"MonthYearNumber"}}}]
